text: But it's more of a surprise.

Sorry for being slow to adopt this. I work a ton lately so there are periods where I'll be slow to respond . My shtick is that I build janky decks and play jank cards. For example, I'm the kind of guy that shows up at the table with Mono Green Multani card draw. I've been playing since 94/95 and I have a soft spot for resolving cards that people are unaware of.
Welcome!
Cool! Are you going to be writing articles, then?
Yeah, he's writing an article series about cool cards from older, forgotten sets.

It's different I assure you. I focus more on building deliberately with jank. Say you wanted to build Ertai, the Corrupted and needed some suggestions.
